{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"alias":"clerkish-cloggy-cod","description":"## Why\nFixedBench's 35-65% over-action result has no gate counterpart: nothing asks whether a change is actually needed. The gate-exempt bug 5886 (one of the three verified misses) is the retrospective test case: its plan asserted a fix for behavior that already worked.\n\n## What\nTwo coupled pieces: (a) a necessity/no-op probe in pass 1 (advisory): does the plan demonstrate the change is needed - current behavior reproduced, existing implementation searched - accepting justified no-op / docs-test-only outcomes; (b) a lightweight bug review tier so gate-exempt bugs get at least the DET floor + necessity probe at claim (today bugs skip plan review entirely). Retrospective gate before landing: the probe fires on 5886's plan. Post-ship validation is DOGFOOD monitoring via R7 (>=1 confirmed catch over the following month, blocking-FP proxy <=10%) - an observation expectation recorded on the ticket, not a config flag or A/B.\n\n## Scope\n- src/rebar/llm/plan_review/ (pass-1 rubric family + the bug-tier claim-gate seam in attest.py/orchestrator) + criteria_routing.json (advisory entry).\n- docs/experiments/plan-review-gate/ retrospective writeup.\n- Sequenced AFTER the floor-split story to avoid routing/kernel conflicts.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Retrospective gate committed before landing: the necessity probe fires on the 5886 plan fixture (pinned as a test) and on >=8/10 E2 unnecessary-mechanism mutants with <=1/10 controls flagged.\n- [ ] The bug review tier runs DET floor + necessity probe on bug claims without adding blocking behavior for bugs, pinned by lifecycle test.\n- [ ] Landed directly in the packaged gate (no config flag); docs/plan-review-gate.md documents the tier and the probe.\n- [ ] [operator-attested] one month of dogfood observation is recorded on this ticket via R7 metrics (catches and FP proxy), whatever the outcome.","id":"03a9-e6d1-4acc-435d","parent_id":"6982-2e75-f8fa-43b9","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"R4: necessity/no-op probe + lightweight bug review tier (gated retrospective)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784143933943723001,"uuid":"73c41ac2-2e7d-4a75-ae4d-374f62bd1bab"}